** Mixing encrypted data with plain YAML **

ansible-vault encrypt_string --help


ansible-vault encrypt_string --vault-password-file "password.sh" --name my_secret
(type into the terminal)
once it says encyption successful, copy and paste the output to a playbook

---
- name: inline secret variable demo
  hosts: localhost
  gather_facts: false

  vars:
    my_secret: !vault |.....(paste in the cipher text)

  task:
    - name: print the secure variable
      debug:
        var: my_secret


Now run the play using the password:
ansible-playbook -i localhost --vault-password-file "password.sh" test.yml
